extends EventMention
    A text string that refers to a (Procedure) Event. This is from the UMLS semantic group of Procedures (except that Laboratory procedures are separate). Based on generic Clinical Element Models (CEMs) Updated by JCasGen Wed Sep 30 11:06:15 EDT 2015 XML source: /Users/pei/workspace/apache-ctakes/3.2.2/ctakes-ytex-uima/target/jcasgen/typesystem.xml
